; handle_common_options indirection (L29544 [general] call site shares parser
; with L28671 per-peer call site) + chan_sip.c:29539 verbatim default-init
; via ast_clear_flag(global_flags[1], SIP_PAGE2_IGNORESDPVERSION) + sip.h:325
; verbatim flag bit (1<<16) + chan_sip.c:10310-10330 verbatim use site at
; process_sdp.
