; Pattern 12 honest-disclosure 24th-instance + chan_sofia-architectural-
; divergence sub-pattern 5th-instance partial-feature-parity flavor (joins
; subscribemwi 17th + notifyringing 19th + autocreatepeer 20th + ignoresdpversion
; 23rd). KNOWN LIMITATION: NO state degrades to NEVER behavior under chan_sofia
; Option B partial wire-in. chan_sip's NO-state semantic ("after-progress-sent
; in-band 2nd-call behavior") requires SIP_PROGRESS_SENT per-pvt state-tracking
; infrastructure — chan_sofia ABSENT today. Operators wanting full chan_sip
; NO-state semantic must wait for future-fix follow-up (~30 LoC pvt->progress_
; sent state-tracking).
;
; Operator action items:
;   * progressinband=never operators: drop-in compat zero-rewrite (chan_sofia
;     intrinsic baseline matches; current chan_sofia behavior preserved)
;   * progressinband=yes operators: drop-in compat zero-rewrite (chan_sofia
;     Option B wire-in returns -1 forcing in-band audio per chan_sip verbatim)
;   * progressinband=no operators: parse-clean migration; effective behavior
