; key OR-chained parser ast_true + chan_sip.c:29531 verbatim default-init via
; DEFAULT_MATCHEXTERNADDRLOCALLY (FALSE per sip.h:210) + sip.h:701 verbatim
; int field + chan_sip.c:4015-4024 verbatim use site at NAT-detection logic
; (peer-outside-localnet AND our-IP-inside-localnet check).
