; Pattern 12 honest-disclosure 30th-instance + chan_sofia-architectural-
; divergence sub-pattern 10th-sub-instance post-PROVEN (joins subscribemwi
; 17th + notifyringing 19th + autocreatepeer 20th + ignoresdpversion 23rd +
