; Pattern 12 honest-disclosure 31st-instance + chan_sofia-architectural-
; divergence sub-pattern 11-sub-instances post-PROVEN (joins subscribemwi
; 17th + notifyringing 19th + autocreatepeer 20th + ignoresdpversion 23rd
