; --- faxdetect (post-T56 chan_sip parity, PARSE-COMPAT-ONLY 4-state multi-mode) ---
; chan_sip semantic: 4-state fax detection trigger flag (no/cng/t38/cng,t38/yes).
; When set, chan_sip detects inband fax CNG tones (via ast_dsp DSP_FEATURE_FAX_
; DETECT) AND/OR T.38 reinvite from peer; auto-switches call to fax handling.
; Multi-mode parser: yes → BOTH (cng+t38); no → NONE; comma-separated cng/t38
; → bit-OR combo. Default no (NONE).
