; chan_sip parity citations: chan_sip.c:28202-28221 verbatim multi-mode parser
; via handle_common_options shared parser (per-peer L28671 + [general] L29544
; both reach same parser) + sip.h:341-344 verbatim 2-bit flag encoding (00=
; NONE / 01=CNG / 10=T38 / 11=BOTH) + chan_sip.c:29536 verbatim default-init
; via ast_clear_flag = NONE + 5+ active use sites L4945 enable_dsp_detect
; (DSP_FEATURE_FAX_DETECT when CNG flag) + L6282 T.38 reinvite trigger
; ast_clear_flag + L8186-8259 sip_rtp_read sets faxdetect=1 when DSP detects
; CNG tone + L8288 post-rtp-read handler triggers fax/T.38 reinvite when CNG
; flag + L10196 T38 reinvite check from peer.
;
; Backup-fork verification (chan_sip.c.bk L4856+L6249+L8047+L8120+L8149+
; L10057+L27963) CONFIRMED chan_sip-parity-NOT-fork-regression-class.
;
; Pattern 12 honest-disclosure 32nd-instance + chan_sofia-architectural-
; divergence sub-pattern 12-sub-instances post-PROVEN (joins subscribemwi
; 17th + notifyringing 19th + autocreatepeer 20th + ignoresdpversion 23rd +
; progressinband 24th-partial + subscribe_network_change_event 25th +
; rtcachefriends 27th + rtautoclear 28th + promiscredir 29th +
; matchexternaddrlocally 30th + autoframing 31st + this 32nd — sub-pattern
; at 12 sub-instances all post-PROVEN N=3 threshold; sub-pattern stability
; strongly validated; TEMPLATE-RIPE).
;
; chan_sofia design rationale: DSP infrastructure PRESENT (T26 inband DTMF
; detection at chan_sofia.c:1795+ sofia_enable_dsp_detect helper + DSP_
; FEATURE_FAX_DETECT API available via gabpbx-core); however chan_sofia T26
; doxygen at L1798 EXPLICITLY documents "fax CNG detection deferred to T.38
; future task per R8" — established operator-honest deferral baseline. T.38
; reinvite infrastructure ABSENT (per pending T.38 LARGE deferred task; no
; T.38 SDP handler in sofia_parse_sdp; no nua_invite re-INVITE T.38 trigger).
; PARSE-COMPAT-ONLY ship: parse + store + display but NO behavioral wire-in.
;
; SS6 (2026-04-28) — 55d4444 KNOWN LIMITATION CLOSED: faxdetect=yes/cng/t38/
; cng,t38 now BEHAVIORAL — DSP_FEATURE_FAX_DETECT enabled per peer when
; faxdetect=cng (or cng,t38); ast_dsp_process emits AST_FRAME_DTMF subclass
; 'f' on CNG tone detection → sofia_read async-gotos channel into "fax"
; extension (chan_sip.c:8288 verbatim). Peer T.38 reINVITE arrival when
; faxdetect=t38 (or cng,t38) → sofia_parse_sdp async-gotos channel into
; "fax" extension (chan_sip.c:10196 verbatim). Dialplan fax extension runs
; SendFAX/ReceiveFAX which negotiates T.38 mode via setoption / control-
; frame chain (sofia_queryoption AST_OPTION_T38_STATE handler at SS5).
;
; Operator action items (post-SS6 BEHAVIORAL wire-in 2026-04-28):
;   * operators with chan_sip faxdetect=yes/no/cng/t38/cng,t38 migrate
;     verbatim zero-rewrite — chan_sip-parity behavior preserved END-TO-END
;   * faxdetect=cng triggers DSP-based CNG tone detection on inbound audio;
;     CNG-detected → async-goto channel to "fax" extension; dialplan
;     SendFAX/ReceiveFAX runs T.38 negotiation
;   * faxdetect=t38 triggers async-goto channel to "fax" extension on peer
;     T.38 reINVITE arrival; dialplan handles T.38 receive
;   * faxdetect=cng,t38 (or yes) enables BOTH triggers
;   * operators NOT setting faxdetect get default no (NONE) = chan_sip drop-
;     in baseline preserved
;
; Production .193 sofia.conf line faxdetect=no (chan_sip drop-in default
; semantic preserved; finally honored on next reload as parse-clean
; migration matching operator intent — REAL OPERATOR DRIVER consummated).
;
; Operator-honest reload-required note: changing faxdetect= requires
; `module reload chan_sofia.so` to update parsed value (no behavioral
; effect — chan_sofia continues current behavior).
;
;faxdetect = no            ; default
;faxdetect = yes           ; equivalent to "cng,t38" — enable both modes
;faxdetect = cng           ; CNG tone detection only
;faxdetect = t38           ; T.38 reinvite detection only
;faxdetect = cng,t38       ; BOTH modes (same as "yes")

