; --- mwiexpiry / mwiexpirey / mwi_expiry (post-T56 chan_sip parity, parser-naming-fix) ---
; MWI subscription default expiry seconds. Default 3600 (chan_sip
; DEFAULT_MWI_EXPIRY parity at sip.h:58). atoi value < 1 clamps to 3600.
